---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Pricing | Boat & Rv Guardian">
	<div class="page-header">
		<div class="container">
			<h1>Pricing & Beta Access</h1>
			<p>Enterprise safety shouldn't break the bank.</p>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="container main-content text-center">
		
		<div class="glass-card pricing-card">
			<h2 class="price-title">Software License</h2>
			<div class="price">
				<span class="currency">$</span><span class="amount">0</span><span class="period">/ during beta</span>
			</div>
			<p class="description">The Boat & Rv Guardian dashboard and services are entirely free to use during our beta phase. Afterwards, we will introduce a low-cost model to sustain ongoing development.</p>
			
			<ul class="features-list">
				<li>Full Dashboard Access (Web, Desktop, Mobile)</li>
				<li>Monitor unlimited sensors and smart valves</li>
				<li>Instant critical push notifications anywhere</li>
				<li>Free during beta, low-cost after</li>
			</ul>

			<a href="https://github.com/jgearinger/Boat-RV-Guardian" class="btn btn-primary btn-large">View Source Code</a>
		</div>

		<section class="hardware-costs glass-card">
			<h2>Estimated Hardware Costs</h2>
			<p>Because the software is free, your only cost is the physical hardware. Here is a typical estimated budget for outfitting a vessel or RV:</p>
			
			<div class="cost-table">
				<div class="cost-row header">
					<div>Component</div>
					<div>Estimated Cost</div>
				</div>
				<div class="cost-row">
					<div>LinkTap Gateway + G2S Smart Valve</div>
					<div>~$150 - $180</div>
				</div>
				<div class="cost-row">
					<div>Shelly Flood Sensor (x2)</div>
					<div>~$60</div>
				</div>
				<div class="cost-row">
					<div>Shelly Plus Uni (for 12V monitoring)</div>
					<div>~$20</div>
				</div>
				<div class="cost-row total">
					<div><strong>Estimated Total</strong></div>
					<div><strong>~$230 - $260</strong></div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<p style="margin-top: 1rem; font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-muted);">*Prices are estimates and vary by region and retailer.</p>
		</section>

	</div>
</Layout>

<style>
	.page-header {
		background: rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.05);
		border-bottom: 1px solid var(--surface-border);
		padding: 4rem 0;
		margin-bottom: 4rem;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.page-header h1 {
		font-size: 3rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		color: #fff;
	}

	.page-header p {
		font-size: 1.2rem;
		color: var(--text-muted);
		max-width: 600px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.text-center {
		text-align: center;
	}

	.pricing-card {
		max-width: 600px;
		margin: 0 auto 4rem;
		padding: 4rem 3rem;
		background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.1) 0%, rgba(255,255,255,0.02) 100%);
		border-top: 4px solid var(--accent-color);
	}

	.price-title {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		color: var(--text-muted);
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.price {
		font-size: 5rem;
		font-weight: 800;
		font-family: var(--font-heading);
		color: #fff;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		line-height: 1;
	}

	.currency {
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		vertical-align: super;
		color: var(--text-muted);
	}

	.period {
		font-size: 1.2rem;
		color: var(--text-muted);
		font-weight: normal;
	}

	.description {
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	.features-list {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
		margin: 0 auto 3rem;
		text-align: left;
		display: inline-block;
	}

	.features-list li {
		padding: 0.5rem 0;
		border-bottom: 1px solid var(--surface-border);
		position: relative;
		padding-left: 2rem;
	}

	.features-list li::before {
		content: "✓";
		position: absolute;
		left: 0;
		color: var(--success-color);
		font-weight: bold;
	}

	.btn-large {
		padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		width: 100%;
		display: block;
	}

	.hardware-costs {
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		text-align: left;
	}

	.hardware-costs h2 {
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.cost-table {
		margin-top: 2rem;
		border: 1px solid var(--surface-border);
		border-radius: 8px;
		overflow: hidden;
	}

	.cost-row {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: space-between;
		padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
		border-bottom: 1px solid var(--surface-border);
	}

	.cost-row:last-child {
		border-bottom: none;
	}

	.cost-row.header {
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
		font-weight: bold;
		color: #fff;
	}

	.cost-row.total {
		background: rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.1);
		color: #fff;
		font-size: 1.1rem;
	}
</style>
